prompts.frontCover:
A humorous full-body watercolor illustration of a young couple, Lao Lao and Jordan, based on the reference photo. Lao Lao is a young East Asian woman with long, straight dark hair and round gold-rimmed glasses, wearing a light blue sweatshirt and black pants. She is standing in front, looking slightly overwhelmed but with a loving smile, as she is being comically lifted off the ground in a giant bear hug by Jordan. Jordan is a young man with Southeast Asian features, short dark hair, wearing a tan hoodie and dark maroon pants; he has a huge, gleeful, and exaggeratedly effortful expression as he squeezes his girlfriend. Floating around them are colorful watercolor splotches and little party elements like confetti and streamers, adding to the fun, chaotic birthday vibe. The background is a soft, simple wash of color, keeping the focus on the couple. The entire image is rendered in a flat 2D watercolor style with soft, blended colors, artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic paint bleeds.

In the center of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! You take my breath away... literally."

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
